{"tid":130473,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(telegram) 聽故事樹窿","createTime":"2017-02-22T12:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T07:16:09.000Z","uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce5418576647c096a6bd5511c5326576c1bbd460","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"無論你有咩故事<br />\n咩煩惱<br />\n想搵人9up都無任歡迎<br />\n未必覆得好快<br />\n但一定唔會hea覆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n@ching1999"},{"pid":"a0f20b659000160afe95c9f479b993eedf03ec0e","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eccbf2f372c752ec462eabb21407ee579a3b9eb","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8464dcc48c45286ca37636029335383a2b73b5","tid":130473,"uid":85248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6489bfc8a6e477d629912fcb0a5ebe29e85f43b5","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f885a6ba378e350a458397533ff151d5ecbe55d","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02268ea2818bb42462a4625303798f7e10fe2a7","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d159e894ce703d602746bc017eef1c5ff8a2ed8c","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T19:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb0c803fffddff0944fa0f835b65677561b45e6","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fd1dcbf481ab5aeb64ed839c67df5595bb4f87","tid":130473,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:35:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得我慘過被七個警察打一身"},{"pid":"062d8356ec897b2d5f074df90b2e5d1f7b53951c","tid":130473,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得我慘過被七個警察打一身</blockquote><br />\n咩事呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad64004b9fdd64681e4cc7c1c03e7674ed9f4e5","tid":130473,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得我慘過被七個警察打一身</blockquote><br />\n咩事呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無挑釁皇仁書院1993-1994總領袖生徐紹基及其女友廖紫蕙<br />\n又無改徐紹基花名做吹簫機<br />\n只係在A level 考多佢一個A(其實我都唔想有咁多A架，我考完試仲以為自己唔合格）<br />\n點解佢地在壹週刊偽造訪問《狀元考試考上癮》害我？<br />\n廖紫蕙(記者)都無正式話要訪問我，最初只係同我講我會在團體相中出現<br />\n點知出街時登左一張偷拍到極樣衰既大頭相<br />\n又屈我自己講返工日日如是好悶、唔考試周身痕<br />\n又登左我職級做我上司title<br />\n偽造訪問出街後我打去搵廖對質時有私家偵探幫我錄左音<br />\n廖紫蕙認晒係屈我<br />\n我去記協投訴，記協包庇，我仲俾自稱係編輯既劉細良鬧我無理指控<br />\n而家記協又delete埋網上個投訴紀錄<br />\n劉慧卿議員2014年知道呢件事去信記協要求重新調查及聽由私家偵探錄既錄音帶<br />\n不過記協拒絕<br />\n我又去私隱專員公署投訴<br />\n佢地又曲解法例唔幫我<br />\n我去上訴又請著個衰律師懶懶閒累我輸官司<br />\n我當時有個同學做商業罪案調查科督察<br />\n又唔提我可以報警告佢地偽造文件<br />\n我舊年email俾梁振英重提呢件事又無人理<br />\n我去「敢言」既麥明詩ig 留言求助<br />\n佢又唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我因為呢件事<br />\n返工見到有問題既野唔敢出聲<br />\n驚上司用偽造訪問事件激到我發癲<br />\n不過最後都無左份工<br />\n暗戀既女仔要告我性騷擾<br />\n阿媽話鍊死我好過養到我咁大<br />\n最後壓力大到想自殺<br />\n去睇精神科仲衰<br />\n喊到收唔到聲<br />\n跟住阿媽無端端同我講耶穌<br />\n搞到我痴埋線<br />\n以為世界末日將至<br />\n十七年黎搵過好多傳媒<br />\n只得大公報肯在2014年報導過兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第四權仲惡過警權<br />\n警察最多打你一身<br />\n傳媒枝筆害到人家破人亡<br />\n最慘係投訴無門<br />\n我無左份工之後只能做派傳單、公仔人<br />\n精神情況最差時要做庇護工場<br />\n而家好番d先可以做兼職保安"}]}